channel.title: I got a new laptop!
channel.description:
I got a new laptop Tuesday night. I ended up getting the Compaq CQ50-108CA, and I think it is actually pretty good for the price of $549.99.
Here are a few pictures of it, seeing as it looking nice, was an absolute bonus. :D
[img]http://www.bestbuy.ca/multimedia/products/large/10108501.jpg[/img] [img]http://www.bestbuy.ca/multimedia/products/large/10108501_left.jpg[/img] [img]http://www.bestbuy.ca/multimedia/products/large/10108501_right.jpg[/img] [img]http://www.bestbuy.ca/multimedia/products/large/10108501_alt.jpg[/img]
It features a AMD Athlon X2 QL-60 Dual-Core Processor, with 2gb, expandable to 3gb RAM, and a Nvidia GeForce 8200M graphics card.
For more information, view this page:
http://www.bestbuy.ca/catalog/proddetail.asp?logon=&langid=EN&sku_id=0926INGFS10108501&catid=25253
What do you guys think? :)
